                                    "TITLE": "Statement Coverage",
                                    "STATEMENT": "The instrumentation shall enable the measurement of statement coverage\n",
                                    "RATIONALE": "Statement coverage is required by DO-178C starting at DAL-C (6.4.4.c)\n",
                                    "RELATIONS": [
